item.description:
Everyone wants to know how much the Cybertruck is going to be, and when you can get one! Well we've got the first Cybertruck Price Calculator available for you to use! Just select your options and click the button to see how much your Cybertruck will cost!

    <h2>Tesla Cybertruck Price Calculator</h2>
    <form id="cybertruckForm">
        <label for="motor">Motor option:</label>
        <select id="motor">
            <option value="1">1 Motor (not available)</option>
            <option value="2">Rear Wheel Drive</option>
            <option value="3">All Wheel Drive</option>
            <option value="4">Cyberbeast</option>
        </select><br><br>

        <label for="battery">Battery Size (heh you don't get to choose):</label>
        <select id="battery">
            <option value="small">Small</option>
            <option value="medium">Medium</option>
            <option value="large">Large</option>
            <option value="stupidLarge">Stupid Large</option>
        </select><br><br>

        <label for="color">Color:</label>
        <select id="color">
            <option value="stainlessSteel">Stainless Steel</option>
            <option value="black">Black</option>
            <option value="white">White</option>
            <option value="custom">Custom</option>
        </select><br><br>

        <button type="button" onclick="calculatePrice()">Calculate Price</button>
    </form>

    <h3 id="result">Total Price: $</h3>

    <script>
        function calculatePrice() {
            // Since the price is always going to be $1 Million, 
            // we don't need to use the selected options for calculation.
            const totalPrice = 1000000;

            // Display the result
            document.getElementById('result').innerHTML = `Total Price: $${totalPrice.toLocaleString()}`;
        }
    </script>

<p><em>*completely unofficial <div style="font-size:.5em">and invalid</div></em></p>

